.SH NAME
help \- Show commands grouped by purpose.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
help
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
Lists registered commands by purpose using the live command registry. Use man(1) for the full manual of one command.
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
$ help
$ man open
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO
man(1)
